Ivie Okujaye Egboh (amụrụ ya na 16 Mee na afọ 1987) ọ bụ onye Naijiria na-eme ihe nkiri, ọ na-emepụta ihe nkiri, Odee edemede, ọgba egwu, ọgụ egwu na onye na-eme ihe ike. N'afọ 2009, Ivie sonyere na asọmpi ihe ngosi TV nke Amstel Malta Box Office (AMBO) ma merie
Mgbe ụfọdụ A na-akpọ ya obere Genevieve n'ihi na ọ yiri onye na-eme ihe nkiri Genevieve Nnaji. E nyere ya ihe nweta a kpọrọ Best Young Actor na bekee na omume 8th Africa Movie Academy Awards
